  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://twitter.com/esudog/status/1600298011791601664<br/>\n<br/>\r\n马XX颠覆政权专案阅卷完毕，总的来说挺有意思的，马及同案犯很多是信基督/天主教的(每天圣经不离手并公开播放那种)，然后他们真的线下招兵买马，买“健身用品”也就是枪枝弹药，甚至还真的组团去射击场练习射击来的，总之非常牛逼伍德充沛,不过存在反贼常见问题：国产软件山巅、不太会翻墙、极右阴谋论等<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTAzZWViYjkyOTM1YWJjMTYyZmM1LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e03eebb92935abc162fc5.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e03eebb92935abc162fc5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e03eebb92935abc162fc5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTNjYTAxNWJkZWE5M2RjZTZjYzBlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/53ca015bdea93dce6cc0e.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/53ca015bdea93dce6cc0e.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/53ca015bdea93dce6cc0e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTg2NjhhOTA4NjFlMDdlYmVkY2RhLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e8668a90861e07ebedcda.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e8668a90861e07ebedcda.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e8668a90861e07ebedcda.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
